        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 id="what-ai-assisted-publishing-means-for-operations-managers-building-repeatable-pipelines" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">What AI-assisted publishing means for operations managers building repeatable pipelines</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">AI-assisted publishing is a game-changer for operations managers in Toronto, enabling them to streamline workflows, enhance quality, and boost efficiency. By leveraging AI, managers can automate repetitive tasks, improve handoffs, and ensure consistent outcomes. This approach empowers teams to focus on high-value activities, driving business growth.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">At its core, AI-assisted publishing involves clearly defining ownership, required inputs, expected outcomes, decision criteria, and measurable metrics. By implementing these key aspects, operations managers can build repeatable pipelines that drive success.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="space-y-3">
