        </section>
        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 id="main-framework-and-checklist" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Main framework and checklist</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">To implement AI-assisted publishing effectively, operations managers should follow a structured framework. This includes defining clear ownership, identifying required inputs, outlining expected outcomes, establishing decision criteria, and setting measurable metrics.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">Here&#39;s a comprehensive checklist to guide managers through the implementation process:</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **Owner**: Clearly assign a responsible individual or team for each stage of the publishing process.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **Required Inputs**: Identify and document the necessary information, data, or assets required for each stage.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **Expected Outcomes**: Define the desired results or deliverables for each stage, ensuring they align with business objectives.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **Decision Criteria**: Establish clear, objective criteria for making decisions at each stage, minimizing subjectivity and bias.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **Measurable Metrics**: Set quantifiable indicators to track progress, assess performance, and ensure the AI-assisted publishing process is working as intended.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 id="key-subtopics" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Key subtopics</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">To gain a holistic understanding of AI-assisted publishing, explore the following key subtopics:</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **AI-assisted Publishing Workflow**: Dive into the detailed steps and stages of an effective AI-assisted publishing process, from planning to distribution.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **Best Practices**: Learn from industry experts and successful implementations to adopt proven strategies and avoid common pitfalls.</p>
          <p class="text-foreground/75">- **FAQ**: Find answers to frequently asked questions about AI-assisted publishing, helping you address challenges and make informed decisions.</p>
